comments.body:
@mccalluc You are correct that the purpose of this PR is not to test software functionality exactly. It is instead to validate that our re-description process is correct (i.e., "Has Tyler received enough training in DataCite from the RDOS team that he can re-describe these records the way they would?") and also to validate that our metadata mapping process is correct (i.e., "Given the form we've created, do we produce a complete and correct DataCite record, as judged by our subject matter experts in RDOS?") 

The epic is here: https://github.com/pulibrary/pdc_describe/issues/229

Once the data migration process is complete we probably won't keep all of these migration specs.
